{"tid":935467,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我知錯了我願意改","createTime":"2018-12-10T04:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T07:09:02.000Z","uid":208280,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4629f60e3b5c8bc8f2c2bf9dcfd79825e5926e6","tid":935467,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日為小小嘢吵，女朋友終於頂唔順話暫時分開，然後我一衝動就話分手吧，宜家好後悔好後悔，諗咗好多日，覺得自己好幼稚，亦都下定決心想改變自己，唔係為佢改，係為自己改。我琴晚搵返佢，佢都願意理我仲打電話畀我，然後我話畀知我嘅諗法，但喺我都明一時半刻佢好難原諒我，之後佢問咗一句，如果復合唔到做返朋友可以嗎？之後我沉默咗一陣，話等我有改變再講好嗎？但喺我唔明佢咩意思，係真係對我絕望咗定係想測試我有冇改變，我真係唔想失去佢，好後悔啊，都奉勸各位，好好珍惜身邊人，就算吵交，都唔好將難聽嘅說話畀對方聽，有時傷到心真係會好痛。我都希望我自己真係有改變，做好自己，唔再令佢失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3db463e4e8fd2aebf93833b8d1d68d02562b72e","tid":935467,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"做返朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵另一條女啦"},{"pid":"7e3c94b5f8b5fc2a330738facaf9396efc403810","tid":935467,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3db463e4e8fd2aebf93833b8d1d68d02562b72e","tid":935467,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"做返朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵另一條女啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係想同佢係一起"},{"pid":"cd253e839e46b73493aa7aee606e4a9399ab3ed7","tid":935467,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e3c94b5f8b5fc2a330738facaf9396efc403810","tid":935467,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3db463e4e8fd2aebf93833b8d1d68d02562b72e","tid":935467,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"做返朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵另一條女啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10